snippet: With the U.S. third-quarter earnings season almost at an end, many investors are breathing a sigh of relief as more companies surpassed profit expectations than in any quarter since 2010....

headline.print_headline: Earnings Outlook Might Be Less Rosy Than Investors Think
headline.main: Earnings Outlook Might Be Less Rosy Than Investors Think

lead_paragraph: With the U.S. third-quarter earnings season almost at an end, many investors are breathing a sigh of relief as more companies surpassed profit expectations than in any quarter since 2010.
